[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you, <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, want to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">come back</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cif you want to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">come back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">must</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">get</st> those <st data-num=\"08251\" class=\"\">disgusting idols</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">out</st> of my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">sight</st><p class=\"poetry\">and must <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no longer</st> <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">go astray</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You must be <st data-num=\"0571\" class=\"\">truthful</st>, <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">honest</st>, and <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">upright</st><p class=\"poetry\">when you <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">take an oath</st> saying, \u2018As surely as the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">lives</st>!\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">If you do,<n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> will <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">pray to be</st> as <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">blessed</st> by him as you are<p class=\"poetry\">and will <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">make</st> him <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">the object of</st> their <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boasting</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Yes</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">this</st> is what the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <p class=\"poetry\">to the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>: <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05214\" class=\"\">Break up</st> your <st data-num=\"05215\" class=\"\">unplowed ground</st>, do <st data-num=\"0408\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02232\" class=\"\">cast seeds</st> <st data-num=\"0413\">among</st> <st data-num=\"06975\">thorns</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04135\" class=\"\">Commit yourselves</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05493 06190\">dedicate</st> your <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">hearts</st> to me<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">Otherwise</st>, my <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">anger</st> will <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">blaze up</st> like a <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">flaming</st> <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> against you<p class=\"poetry\">that <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one will be able to <st data-num=\"03518\" class=\"\">extinguish</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">That will happen <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">because of</st> the <st data-num=\"07455\" class=\"\">evil</st> you have <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">done</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">Announce</st><n id=\"2\" /> this in <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"08085 0559\">proclaim</st> it in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>:<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"08628\" class=\"\">Sound</st> the <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">trumpet</st><n id=\"4\" /> throughout the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>!\u2019<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">Shout</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">out</st> <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">loudly</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">Gather together</st>! Let us <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">flee</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> the <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortified</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st>!\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">Raise</st> a <st data-num=\"05251\" class=\"\">signal flag</st> that tells people to go to <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05756\" class=\"\">Run for safety</st>! Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">delay</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am about to <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> out of the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It will bring <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Like a <st data-num=\"0738\" class=\"\">lion</st> that has <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">come up</st> from its <st data-num=\"05441\" class=\"\">lair</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the one who <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroys</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> has <st data-num=\"05265\" class=\"\">set out</st> from his <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">home base</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He is <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">coming out</st> to <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">lay</st> your <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">waste</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> will <st data-num=\"05327\" class=\"\">become ruins</st> and lie <st data-num=\"0369 03427\">uninhabited</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 02063\">So</st> <st data-num=\"02296\" class=\"\">put on</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05594\" class=\"\">Mourn</st> and <st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">wail</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">saying</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018The <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">fierce</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><p class=\"poetry\">has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turned away</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> us!\u2019<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03117 01931\">When</st> this <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">happens</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cthe <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and his <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">lose</st> their <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">courage</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> will <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">be struck with horror</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> will <st data-num=\"08539\" class=\"\">be speechless in astonishment</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">In response to all this<n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0162\" class=\"\">Ah</st>, <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<n id=\"2\" /> you have <st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">surely</st> <st data-num=\"05377\" class=\"\">allowed</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"4\" /> to be <st data-num=\"05377\" class=\"\">deceived</st> by those who <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018You will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">safe</st>!\u2019<n id=\"5\" /> But in fact a <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> <st data-num=\"05060\" class=\"\">is</st> already <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">at</st> our <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">throats</st>.\u201d<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"1\" /> will be <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cA <st data-num=\"06703\" class=\"\">scorching</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st> will sweep down<p class=\"poetry\">from the <st data-num=\"08205\" class=\"\">hilltops</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">on</st><n id=\"2\" /> my <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">dear</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">It will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be a gentle breeze<p class=\"poetry\">for <st data-num=\"02219\" class=\"\">winnowing</st><n id=\"4\" /> the grain and <st data-num=\"01305\" class=\"\">blowing away</st> the chaff.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">No,<n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st> too <st data-num=\"04392\" class=\"\">strong</st> for <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">that</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> at my bidding.<p class=\"poetry\">Yes, <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">even</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, myself, am <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">calling down</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judgment</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">on</st> them.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>! The enemy is <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">approaching</st> like <st data-num=\"06051\" class=\"\">gathering clouds</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The roar of his <st data-num=\"04818\" class=\"\">chariots</st> is like that of a <st data-num=\"05492\" class=\"\">whirlwind</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">His <st data-num=\"05483\" class=\"\">horses</st> <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">move</st> more <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">swiftly</st> than <st data-num=\"05404\" class=\"\">eagles</st>.\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">I cry out,<n id=\"3\" /> \u201cWe are <st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">doomed</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> we will be <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">O people of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>, <st data-num=\"03526\" class=\"\">purify</st> your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">hearts</st> from <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">so that</st> you may yet be <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">delivered</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704 04970\">How long</st> will you <st data-num=\"03885\" class=\"\">continue to harbor up</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">schemes</st> <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">within</st> you?</p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">messengers</st> are <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">coming</st>, <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heralding</st> <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">disaster</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">from the city of <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan</st> and from the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hills</st> of <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They are saying,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">Announce</st> to the surrounding <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018The <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">enemy is coming</st>!\u2019<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Proclaim</st> this message<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018Those who <st data-num=\"05341\" class=\"\">besiege</st> cities<n id=\"5\" /> are <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st> from a <st data-num=\"04801\" class=\"\">distant</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They are ready to <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">raise</st> the battle <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">cry</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st><n id=\"6\" /> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> in <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"01961 05921 05439\">surround</st> Jerusalem<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like men <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">guarding</st> a <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">field</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"04784\" class=\"\">rebelled against</st> me,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> you have lived and the <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">things</st> you have <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">done</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">this</st> on you.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">This</st> is the <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">punishment</st> you deserve, and it will be <st data-num=\"04751\" class=\"\">painful</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">indeed</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">The pain will be so bad</st> it will <st data-num=\"05060 05704\">pierce</st> your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cOh, the feeling in the <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">pit</st> of my <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">stomach</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"02342\" class=\"\">writhe in anguish</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Oh, the <st data-num=\"07023\">pain</st> <st data-num=\"07023\" class=\"\">in</st> my <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st> <st data-num=\"01993\" class=\"\">pounds</st> within me.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"02790\" class=\"\">keep silent</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of the <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">trumpet</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the sound of the <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> <st data-num=\"08643\" class=\"\">cry</st> pierces my <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">soul</st>!<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I see<n id=\"1\" /> one <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">after</st> <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">another</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">taking place</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">so that</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">lies in ruins</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I see our<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tents</st> <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">suddenly</st> <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">their<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03407\" class=\"\">curtains</st> torn down in a mere <st data-num=\"07281\" class=\"\">instant</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704 04970\">How long</st> must I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> the enemy\u2019s <st data-num=\"05251\" class=\"\">battle flags</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> the military <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">signals</st> of their <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">bugles</st>?\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> answered,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThis will happen<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0191\" class=\"\">are foolish</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">They</st> are like <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st> <st data-num=\"05530\" class=\"\">who have no sense</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">They</st> have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understanding</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">They</st> are <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">skilled</st> at <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">doing evil</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know how</st> to <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">do good</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">looked at</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">saw</st><n id=\"1\" /> that it was an <st data-num=\"08414\" class=\"\">empty</st> <st data-num=\"0922\" class=\"\">wasteland</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I looked up <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st>, and its <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">light</st> had <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">vanished</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"07200\">looked at</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">saw</st> that they were <st data-num=\"07493\" class=\"\">shaking</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st> <st data-num=\"07043\">were swaying back and forth</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">looked</st> and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">saw</st> that <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there were no</st> more <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and that <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05775\" class=\"\">birds</st> in the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> had <st data-num=\"05074\" class=\"\">flown away</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">looked</st> and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">saw</st> that the <st data-num=\"03759\" class=\"\">fruitful land</st> had become a <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st><p class=\"poetry\">and that <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> had been <st data-num=\"05422\" class=\"\">laid in ruins</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">brought this all about</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">because of</st> his <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">blazing</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">All this will happen <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">desolate</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">however, I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03617 06213\">completely destroy</st> it.</p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">Because of</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> will <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st><p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> <st data-num=\"04605\" class=\"\">above</st> will <st data-num=\"06937\" class=\"\">grow black</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03588\">For</st> I have <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">made</st> my <st data-num=\"02161\" class=\"\">purpose</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">known</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">relent</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turn back</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> carrying it out.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">At the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of the approaching <st data-num=\"06571\" class=\"\">horsemen</st> and <st data-num=\"07411 07198\">archers</st><p class=\"poetry\">the people of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">town</st> will <st data-num=\"01272\" class=\"\">flee</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Some of them will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">hide</st> in the <st data-num=\"05645\" class=\"\">thickets</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Others will <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">climb up</st> among the <st data-num=\"03710\" class=\"\">rocks</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> will be <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">deserted</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> will <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">remain</st> in <st data-num=\"02004\" class=\"\">them</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">And <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, Zion, city <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">doomed to destruction</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">accomplish</st> <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">nothing</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"03847\" class=\"\">wearing</st> a <st data-num=\"08144\" class=\"\">beautiful dress</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05710\" class=\"\">decking</st> yourself <st data-num=\"05710\" class=\"\">out</st> in <st data-num=\"05716\" class=\"\">jewels</st> of <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">putting on</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eye</st> <st data-num=\"06320\" class=\"\">shadow</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You are <st data-num=\"03302\" class=\"\">making</st> yourself <st data-num=\"03302\" class=\"\">beautiful</st> for <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">nothing</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"05689\" class=\"\">lovers</st> <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">spurn</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">want to kill</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">you</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">In fact</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> a <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">cry</st> like that of a <st data-num=\"02342\" class=\"\">woman in labor</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">cry of anguish</st> like that of a <st data-num=\"01069\" class=\"\">woman giving birth to her first baby</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It is the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">cry</st> of <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03306\" class=\"\">gasping for breath</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">reaching out</st> <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">for help</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> saying, \u201cI am <st data-num=\"0188 04994\">done in</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">life</st> is <st data-num=\"05888\" class=\"\">ebbing away</st> before these <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">murderers</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  }
]